{"prayers":[{"phelps":"BH11209","text":"Neepawee steemoke, nedawee non say Mantou, keyooma ay cueseeheen keekag skayntag kaymee haystatak. Neepawee steemoke, mayquatchooma omah may quatska may swatsian aykooma kee ma skowsyooin, aykoomooma un toomaxion keeway yootsin.  Keyooma poko say Mantou mawiyuk gootak, aywee geehiac geeway gagoos dadegwak, weeah, poko enna kahtoe gahtsuk.\n\n* I bear witness, O my God, that Thou hast created me to know Thee and to worship Thee. I testify, at this moment, to my powerlessness and to Thy might, to my poverty and to Thy wealth.\n* There is none other God but Thee, the Help in Peril, the Self-Subsisting.","name":"Short Obligatory Prayer","category":"Cree","order_in_cat":1,"source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"3be2a82f-6dfe-4149-b976-11afe83bc64f","v":"3jmsab4c400zdlgy3ha2a39sf","book":"nai-CA:bp","book_cats":{"af:bp":{"cat":"Kort verpligte gebed","order_in_cat":1},"am:bp":{"cat":"አጭሩ (Short)","order_in_cat":1},"ar:bp":{"cat":"الصلاة   الصغيرة","order_in_cat":1},"az:bp":{"cat":"Qısa Namaz","order_in_cat":1},"be:bp":{"cat":"Кароткая абавязковая малітва","order_in_cat":1},"bg:bp":{"cat":"Кратка задължителна молитва","order_in_cat":1},"bi:bp":{"cat":"SOTFALA  OBLIGATORI  PREA","order_in_cat":1},"bs:bp":{"cat":"Kratka Obavezna Molitva","order_in_cat":1},"ca:bp":{"cat":"Oració obligatòria curta","order_in_cat":1},"co:bp":{"cat":"Preghera dì tutti i ghjorni","order_in_cat":1},"cs:bp":{"cat":"Krátká denní modlitba","order_in_cat":1},"cy:bp":{"cat":"Short Obligatory Prayer","order_in_cat":1},"da:bp":{"cat":"Kort Obligatorisk Bøn","order_in_cat":1},"de:bp":{"cat":"Das kurze Pflichtgebet","order_in_cat":1},"dgz:bp":{"cat":"Marek Iyanupe U’uraewa (Short Obligatory Prayer)","order_in_cat":1},"el:bp":{"cat":"ΜΙΚΡΗ ΥΠΟΧΡΕΩΤΙΚΗ ΠΡΟΣΕΥΧΗ","order_in_cat":1},"en:bp":{"cat":"Short Obligatory Prayer","order_in_cat":1},"eo:bp":{"cat":"Devigaj Preĝoj - La Mallonga","order_in_cat":1},"es:bp":{"cat":"Oración obligatoria corta","order_in_cat":1},"eu:bp":{"